    THEN 0 ELSE [i.Branch].[FirmId]
END AS [FirmId]
FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [i]

WHERE [i].[Id] = @__userId_0

SELECT TOP(1) [i].[Id] AS [_Id], [i].[Name], [i].[ImagePath], COALESCE([i].[BranchId], 0) AS [BranchId], [i].[Email], [i].[IsActive], [i].[PhoneNumber] AS [Phone], CASE
    WHEN [i].[BranchId] IS NULL
    THEN 0 ELSE [i.Branch].[FirmId]
END AS [FirmId]
FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [i]

WHERE [i].[Id] = @__userId_0

SELECT TOP(1) [i].[Id] AS [_Id], [i].[Name], [i].[ImagePath], COALESCE([i].[BranchId], 0) AS [BranchId], [i].[Email], [i].[IsActive], [i].[PhoneNumber] AS [Phone], CASE

    THEN 0 ELSE [i.Branch].[FirmId]
END AS [FirmId]
